ruby-mysql
------------------------------------------
Ruby bindings for the MySQL client library.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.20-1
  libmysqlclient15-5.0.22-1
  ruby-1.8.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  cygwin-1.5.20-1
  binutils-20050610-1
  cygport-0.2.2-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-1
  make-3.80-1
  ruby-1.8.4-1

Canonical website:
  http://www.tmtm.org/en/mysql/ruby/

Canonical download:
  http://tmtm.org/downloads/mysql/ruby/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ruby-mysql-2.7.1-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ruby-mysql-2.7.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ruby-mysql-2.7.1-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ruby-mysql-2.7.1-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/mysql.so
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ruby-mysql-2.7.1.README
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-mysql-2.7.1/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-mysql-2.7.1/COPYING.ja
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-mysql-2.7.1/html/README.html
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-mysql-2.7.1/html/README_ja.html

------------------

Port Notes:

